name: TrackMyBills
0:
”Alexa, launch track my bills”
”Alexa, ask track my bills to add a bill”
”Alexa, ask track my bills to get total”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: track my bills
des:
Just enable this skill on your device and start keep track of your monthly bills. No need to open an account, no need to use your mobile phone apps to manual enter the bills. Just talk to the skill
and let the skill do the work for you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
